icle computing.", "Microsoft is an American technology company founded by Bill Gates in 1975 and headquartered in Redmond, Washington. It developed the Windows operating system, Office productivity suite, and the Azure cloud computing platform."], "scores": [0.6890471410110176, 0.44461646214225264, 0.3725370480832725, 0.35936831066906433, 0.35775208432273076], "model_name": "mpnet", "document_ids": ["Apple", "Intel", "IBM", "Nvidia", "Microsoft"]}}